# Sample SSH server configuration

Port 22
Protocol 2

HostKeyAlgorithms ssh-ed25519,ssh-rsa,ecdsa-sha2-nistp256
KexAlgorithms curve25519-sha256,diffie-hellman-group14-sha256,diffie-hellman-group16-sha512
Ciphers aes256-gcm@openssh.com,aes128-gcm@openssh.com,chacha20-poly1305@openssh.com,aes256-ctr,aes128-ctr
MACs hmac-sha2-256,hmac-sha2-512
